    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hello!</p>

<p>It's a bit of internal incompatibility due fact that Zend_Rest_Client supports PUT/GET/DELETE/POST methods, but Zend_Rest_Server only GET/POST.</p>

<p>I can do HTTP rest request "DELETE /rest/object/123", but processing it via  Zend_Rest_Server is impossible.
Adding suppport for using  HTTP method and making GET/POST "method" argument optional, would be quite an improvement.</p>

<p>Cheers!</p>

